[[File:HidingAmongEnemies-TCGNA.png|thumb|right|250px|The ''Millennium Falcon'' attached to the con tower of an Imperial Star Destroyer]]
A '''landing claw''' was a magnetic or mechanical gripping device found on [[Starship/Legends|starships]] throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] that adhered to almost any surface. Landing claws were used when ships needed to secure themselves to areas that would not normally be considered as appropriate landing zones including, for instance, the command tower of an [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial''-class Star Destroyer]].

The [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']] was equipped with such a device.

